    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>gochujang </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>mirin</strong> to a bowl with a knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Put the bowl in the <strong>microwave </strong>for 30 secs or until the butter has melted – this is your <strong>bibimbap sauce</strong></p>",
