    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>cooked rice</strong> in a bowl and top with the <strong>crispy mackerel</strong>, <strong>quick-pickled smashed cucumber</strong> and <strong>mooli slaw</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>bibimbap sauce</strong></p><p>Garnish with your <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Tip: To eat this the Korean way, give everything a mix up to coat it all in the bibimbap sauce</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
